comment: ggZH  xsec  is  from  https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/LHCPhysics/CERNYellowReportPageAt1314TeV2014.    However  some  older  numbers  I  have  from  HXSWG  give  1.227E-01  as  the  box  xsec.    If  you  multiply  by  the  ratio  (triangle+box+int)/box  from  JHUGen  you  get  0.02801.    (JHUGen  does  not  provide  absolute  xsecs.    But  its  ratios  are  correct.)    I  am  not  sure  if  they  use  box  only  in  the  way  I  interpret  it.    I  will  go  with  the  former  number  which  is  more  in  line  with  what  I  expect.
